AUDIO: 'metal processes. &gt;&gt; [music] &gt;&gt; I\'ll leave the details of the coupon below. So now to make Walter a true workshop companion, let\'s give him the ability to hear and speak. So what I\'m going to do now is test a few phrases that I programmed [music] specifically'

